title: Number of homicides in Sweden 2008 to 2018
summary: In general Number of homicides has rose over the Year.
Number of homicides is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2013, roughly constant from 2013 to 2014, gradually increasing from 2014 to 2015, and lastly roughly constant from 2015 to 2016.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Number of homicides, about 112.0 was reported at Year 2015
The lowest Number of homicides, of value 68.0 was reported at Year 2012
